{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773352025701,"sessionID":"ses_31bfd801cffeMfcGlS1DXqsNs2","part":{"id":"prt_ce40467ba001HLk4zbFcX20Kfl","sessionID":"ses_31bfd801cffeMfcGlS1DXqsNs2","messageID":"msg_ce4045d8c001K7KE15DSv9LrW3","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01QtVkBwdFA2iJrFGJDPpFx1","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/lib/history.ts src/commands/history.ts && git commit -m \"feat(wave-history-export): add history library and command\n\nAdd src/lib/history.ts with types and I/O for wave history records\nstored in .wombo-history/<wave-id>.json. Includes:\n- WaveHistoryRecord and AgentHistoryRecord types\n- waveStateToHistory() converter from live state\n- exportWaveHistory(), saveHistory(), loadHistory(), listHistory()\n\nAdd src/commands/history.ts with the 'wombo history' command:\n- List all past waves with summary table\n- View detailed wave results with per-agent breakdown\n- Supports --output json for structured output\"","description":"Commit history lib and command files"},"output":"[feature/wave-history-export 653fcdd] feat(wave-history-export): add history library and command\n 2 files changed, 531 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 src/commands/history.ts\n create mode 100644 src/lib/history.ts\n","title":"Commit history lib and command files","metadata":{"output":"[feature/wave-history-export 653fcdd] feat(wave-history-export): add history library and command\n 2 files changed, 531 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 src/commands/history.ts\n create mode 100644 src/lib/history.ts\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit history lib and command files","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773352025656,"end":1773352025701}}}}
