{"type":"text","timestamp":1773352205342,"sessionID":"ses_31bfd801cffeMfcGlS1DXqsNs2","part":{"id":"prt_ce40710650011zbcqSw7R6WOfH","sessionID":"ses_31bfd801cffeMfcGlS1DXqsNs2","messageID":"msg_ce40705af001kIY3y1VFkim47x","type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of everything implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### Feature: Wave History and Summary Export (`wave-history-export`)\n\n**4 commits across 6 files:**\n\n1. **`src/lib/history.ts`** (new) — Core history library:\n   - `WaveHistoryRecord` and `AgentHistoryRecord` types with full schema (feature success/failure, duration, retry counts, merge conflicts, build output)\n   - `waveStateToHistory()` — converts live `WaveState` to a history record with computed summary stats\n   - `exportWaveHistory()` — main entry point for auto-export\n   - `saveHistory()` — atomic write to `.wombo-history/<wave-id>.json`\n   - `loadHistory()` / `listHistory()` — read back individual or all records\n\n2. **`src/commands/history.ts`** (new) — `wombo history` command:\n   - `wombo history` — lists all past waves in a formatted table (wave ID, date, total/ok/fail/merged counts, retries, duration)\n   - `wombo history <wave-id>` — shows detailed wave results with per-agent breakdown (status, retries, duration, build pass/fail, merge conflicts, errors)\n   - `--output json` — outputs full JSON for structured consumption\n\n3. **`src/commands/launch.ts`** (modified) — Auto-export on wave completion in headless mode\n\n4. **`src/commands/resume.ts`** (modified) — Auto-export on wave completion in headless resume mode\n\n5. **`src/index.ts`** (modified) — CLI routing, help text, and usage examples for `history` command\n\n6. **`src/lib/schema.ts`** (modified) — Command registry entry for `wombo describe history`\n\n7. **`.gitignore`** (modified) — Added `.wombo-history/`\n\n8. **`src/commands/cleanup.ts`** (modified) — Documented that `.wombo-history/` is intentionally preserved; added user-facing note\n\n### Constraint Compliance:\n- ✅ Auto-exports on wave completion (both launch and resume headless flows)\n- ✅ Survives cleanup (stored in `.wombo-history/`, not touched by cleanup)\n- ✅ Supports `wombo history` command to list/view past waves\n- ✅ Supports `--output json`\n- ✅ No new dependencies added\n- ✅ Typecheck and build both pass","time":{"start":1773352205342,"end":1773352205342}}}
